{Speech 10}{}{[Вы видите блестящую железную коробку]}
{Speech 10 Answer Exit}{}{Ого!}

[Text engl]
{Name}{}{Mr. Handy}
{DescAliveShort}{}{You see Mr. Handy, the robot.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{It's a real repair Mr. Handy robot.}
{Speech 1}{}{Initial preferences}
{Speech 1 Answer 2}{}{smart}
{Speech 1 Answer 10}{}{dumb}
{Speech 2}{}{[Looks like this robot is out of order]}
{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{[Try to figure out what's wrong with it]}
{Speech 2 Answer 4}{}{[Try to figure out what's wrong with it]}
{Speech 2 Answer 6}{}{Let's try to fix this...}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{What an old piece of junk! [You angrily kick the device]}
{Speech 3}{}{[You fiddle with it for a long time, but still cannot figure out the reason why it's broken]}
{Speech 4}{}{[During examination you notice that it's missing a couple of fuses and that it needs oiling up. Yeah... Seems that you'll need a Super Repair Kit here]}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit}{}{Oops! Okay, I'll search then.}
{Speech 6}{}{[You succesfully install new fuses and change the oil. Mr. Handy is revived and buzzing happily]}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{It works! I'll go tell Smitty.}
{Speech 10}{}{[You see a shiny metal box]}
{Speech 10 Answer Exit}{}{Wow!}
